description: Dept. of Elections - Elected Mr. Nimal Silva Handun as a Member of the Katunayake, Seeduwa U/C, Mr. Kumarasamy Kathirkamanathan as a Member of the Nallur P/S, Mr. Gayan Geethika Thalpe Liyanage as a Member of the Bope-Podala P/S- Ukawaththa Chandima Thero as the Cahiramn of the Bope- Poddala P/S
